                        <note>Text from autopsy, read against Bivona (1994)</note>
                    </app>
                    <app loc="1">
                        <note>Bivona (1994) asserts an unclear 'm' at the end of the visible line 1, but 'a' is equally possible.</note>
                    </app>
                    <app loc="6">
                        <note>Bivona (1994) reads 'ga' at the beginning of the visible line 6, but the 'g' is heavily obscured; potentially an 's' instead.</note>
